<div xml:space="preserve">
<p begin="1062900000t" end="1090400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle0">哥哥 差不多快到达布利斯了</p>
<p begin="1111000000t" end="1122400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle1">做梦了吗</p>
<p begin="1129400000t" end="1154400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle2">嗯 梦到那家伙了</p>
<p begin="1214300000t" end="1236500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle3">终于到了啊</p>
<p begin="1240300000t" end="1248300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle4">嗯</p>
<p begin="1262200000t" end="1283890000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle5">师父要是不在家就好了</p>
<p begin="1286200000t" end="1294790000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle6">嗯…</p>
<p begin="1403700000t" end="1418400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle7">您…您好</p>
<p begin="1420800000t" end="1435800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle8">好久不见了</p>
<p begin="1439500000t" end="1467800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle9">欢迎啊 长大了呢</p>
<p begin="1468800000t" end="1486900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle10">会…会变矮</p>
<p begin="1490700000t" end="1513800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle11">那个…我是阿尔冯斯</p>
<p begin="1519700000t" end="1532800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle12">久疏问候了</p>
<p begin="1558900000t" end="1580300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle13">长大了好多啊</p>
<p begin="1586300000t" end="1620700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle14">变成铠甲之身以后第一次被摸摸头</p>
<p begin="1634000000t" end="1663800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle15">伊兹密 艾尔利克家的小鬼们来了</p>
<p begin="1668400000t" end="1679100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle16">能下床吗</p>
<p begin="1684100000t" end="1712400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle17">没问题 今天感觉还好</p>
<p begin="1721000000t" end="1740900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle18">原来不舒服正躺着呢</p>
<p begin="1743600000t" end="1764600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle19">身体还没好起来啊</p>
<p begin="1892300000t" end="1907800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle20">这个笨徒弟</p>
<p begin="1914000000t" end="1933500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle21">听说你沦为军方走狗了？</p>
<p begin="2002200000t" end="2027100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle22">师父 那个…这个是…</p>
<p begin="2040900000t" end="2071200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle23">阿尔 你长这么高了啊</p>
<p begin="2099600000t" end="2122500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle24">师父倒是没什么变…</p>
<p begin="2163000000t" end="2176600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle25">锻炼得还不够</p>
<p begin="2179900000t" end="2191700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle26">好痛…</p>
<p begin="2192000000t" end="2215200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle27">您不是身体不舒服吗</p>
<p begin="2216000000t" end="2249800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle28">胡说八道 还不是因为你们来了我才…</p>
<p begin="2289600000t" end="2302900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle29">不要太勉强自己啦</p>
<p begin="2312300000t" end="2345500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle30">让你担心了 老公</p>
<p begin="2393900000t" end="2415400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle31">关于贤者之石我没什么造诣</p>
<p begin="2421800000t" end="2434300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle32">因为没兴趣</p>
<p begin="2439200000t" end="2451400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle33">这样啊</p>
<p begin="2463400000t" end="2477800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle34">以前在中央市</p>
<p begin="2481000000t" end="2507500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle35">不是见过一个很了解贤者之石的炼金术师吗</p>
<p begin="2527200000t" end="2537200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle36">是什么人</p>
<p begin="2541500000t" end="2567900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle37">我记得名字叫…</p>
<p begin="2576800000t" end="2588200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle38">霍恩海姆</p>
<p begin="2693800000t" end="2702100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle39">怎么了</p>
<p begin="2713200000t" end="2725500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle40">他还活着啊</p>
<p begin="2732500000t" end="2742300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle41">你认识啊</p>
<p begin="2757700000t" end="2768200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle42">他是我们的父亲</p>
<p begin="2782600000t" end="2798100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle43">就是那个以前就离家出走的啊</p>
<p begin="2804000000t" end="2814800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle44">那个混蛋</p>
<p begin="2839100000t" end="2866100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle45">母亲就是因为那种人才死的</p>
<p begin="2872800000t" end="2887300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle46">就是因为那种人…</p>
<p begin="2941800000t" end="2956900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle47">哎呀 怎么了</p>
<p begin="2960500000t" end="2972700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle48">这么早起来</p>
<p begin="2997000000t" end="3015100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle49">阿尔说要尿尿</p>
<p begin="3019400000t" end="3039100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle50">多亏你照顾阿尔啊</p>
<p begin="3042600000t" end="3056000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle51">谢谢你 爱德</p>
<p begin="3320600000t" end="3337700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle52">对了 爸爸呢</p>
<p begin="3376100000t" end="3386500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle53">出门去了</p>
<p begin="3389500000t" end="3402600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle54">几时回来呢</p>
<p begin="3445700000t" end="3475000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle55">咯吱咯吱咯吱</p>
<p begin="3484700000t" end="3498600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle56">咯吱咯吱咯吱</p>
<p begin="3503600000t" end="3522300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle57">很快就会回来的</p>
<p begin="3527900000t" end="3540400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle58">快吃吧</p>
<p begin="3585900000t" end="3595500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle59">妈妈</p>
<p begin="3617300000t" end="3626700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle60">妈妈</p>
<p begin="3648800000t" end="3657900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle61">妈妈</p>
<p begin="3735700000t" end="3746100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle62">妈妈！</p>
<p begin="3869900000t" end="3903400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle63">那个 关于贤者之石爸爸有没有提到什么</p>
<p begin="3911100000t" end="3953900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle64">说是长年的愿望就快实现了 很开心的样子</p>
<p begin="3987600000t" end="3995400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle65">痛</p>
<p begin="4006300000t" end="4016100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle66">吃饭去</p>
<p begin="4022200000t" end="4034800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle67">是</p>
<p begin="4091600000t" end="4102300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle68">阿尔不吃吗</p>
<p begin="4109000000t" end="4142300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle69">不用 我在火车上吃得很饱了</p>
<p begin="4143600000t" end="4154300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle70">对了 阿尔</p>
<p begin="4156500000t" end="4186700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle71">我们在拉修瓦雷还看到小孩子的出生呢</p>
<p begin="4188200000t" end="4207600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle72">对对 师父</p>
<p begin="4209300000t" end="4239100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle73">我们还帮忙接生呢</p>
<p begin="4241200000t" end="4273200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle74">笨蛋 那根本就不算帮忙啦</p>
<p begin="4283900000t" end="4318300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle75">一家人齐心协力 母亲也非常拼命</p>
<p begin="4320700000t" end="4352000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle76">人是在大家的祝福之下诞生的呀</p>
<p begin="4360200000t" end="4399600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle77">没错 你们也是这样获得了生命</p>
<p begin="4404200000t" end="4425800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle78">要为自己的生命感到骄傲</p>
<p begin="4518900000t" end="4527400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle79">哥哥</p>
<p begin="4542400000t" end="4558100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle80">师父真是一点也没变呢</p>
<p begin="4562500000t" end="4593800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle81">嗯 和当年一模一样</p>
<p begin="4723800000t" end="4731500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle82">坚持住</p>
<p begin="4731700000t" end="4746700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle83">再多拿点沙包来</p>
<p begin="4747200000t" end="4755500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle84">堤坝要垮了</p>
<p begin="4810800000t" end="4837400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle85">决堤了 快往高处逃啊</p>
<p begin="4842300000t" end="4856200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle86">哥哥 你看</p>
<p begin="4901000000t" end="4914000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle87">喂 危险啊</p>
<p begin="5183090000t" end="5200390000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle88">这样应该能撑一段时间了</p>
<p begin="5215100000t" end="5230000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle89">你…你是什么人</p>
<p begin="5237600000t" end="5256800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle90">正巧路过的主妇</p>
<p begin="5324200000t" end="5343800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle91">请收我们为徒吧 阿姨</p>
<p begin="5402700000t" end="5418500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle92">求您了 阿姨</p>
<p begin="5419200000t" end="5450800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle93">阿姨耳背没听清</p>
<p begin="5454900000t" end="5472500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle94">你们再说一遍？</p>
<p begin="5488400000t" end="5504100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle95">刚…刚才那句话收回</p>
<p begin="5504300000t" end="5525400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle96">请收我们为徒吧 大姐姐</p>
<p begin="5526900000t" end="5535100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle97">不行</p>
<p begin="5535800000t" end="5545400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle98">为什么</p>
<p begin="5548900000t" end="5561000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle99">我不收徒弟的</p>
<p begin="5565400000t" end="5578200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle100">而且我还在旅行呢</p>
<p begin="5580200000t" end="5600000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle101">求求您 收我们为徒吧</p>
<p begin="5610500000t" end="5619600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle102">烦死人了</p>
<p begin="5621400000t" end="5632100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle103">你们父母批准了吗</p>
<p begin="5636000000t" end="5664600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle104">那个…他们没有父母的</p>
<p begin="5723200000t" end="5741100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle105">就怕这种的</p>
<p begin="5838100000t" end="5852600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle106">你们俩想办法生存下来吧</p>
<p begin="5870800000t" end="5883500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle107">这是试修行</p>
<p begin="5888900000t" end="5905900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle108">能通过就进入正式修行</p>
<p begin="5911900000t" end="5944600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle109">试修行阶段禁止使用炼金术</p>
<p begin="5962200000t" end="5984000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle110">「一即全 全即一」</p>
<p begin="5989900000t" end="6012100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle111">一个月内想出这句话的解答</p>
<p begin="6021300000t" end="6060100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle112">答不出来就送回里森堡哦</p>
<p begin="6090700000t" end="6098200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle113">闪了</p>
<p begin="6140900000t" end="6194700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle114">这算啥啊～啥啊～</p>
<p begin="6215100000t" end="6234900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle115">肚子饿了</p>
<p begin="6236600000t" end="6258800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle116">好想睡床上啊</p>
<p begin="6331800000t" end="6359600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle117">这算哪门子炼金术修行啊</p>
<p begin="6406800000t" end="6435800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle118">肚子好饿…</p>
<p begin="6507300000t" end="6525300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle119">他们没问题吧</p>
<p begin="6535300000t" end="6560300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle120">实践出真知嘛</p>
<p begin="6568300000t" end="6594300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle121">想要深入了解炼金术的精髓</p>
<p begin="6597300000t" end="6616300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle122">只有那个方法最管用</p>
<p begin="6621300000t" end="6639300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle123">如果这样还什么都学不会</p>
<p begin="6645300000t" end="6669300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle124">他们的才能也就仅此而已</p>
<p begin="6677300000t" end="6695300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle125">我也不会收他们为徒了</p>
<p begin="6725300000t" end="6744300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle126">我担心的是</p>
<p begin="6746300000t" end="6763300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle127">他们的生命安全哎</p>
<p begin="6767300000t" end="6783300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle128">我修行的时候</p>
<p begin="6790300000t" end="6821300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle129">可是在严冬的布里格斯山（Briggs）困了一个月哦</p>
<p begin="6830300000t" end="6855300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle130">一般人哪能跟你比呀</p>
<p begin="6858300000t" end="6878300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle131">那个岛上食物丰富</p>
<p begin="6881300000t" end="6895300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle132">肯定死不了啦</p>
<p begin="6932300000t" end="6945300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle133">抓住啦</p>
<p begin="6959300000t" end="6978300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle134">这个要怎么吃啊</p>
<p begin="6992300000t" end="7002300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle135">咔嚓一刀</p>
<p begin="7005300000t" end="7015300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle136">咔嚓…</p>
<p begin="7112300000t" end="7136300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle137">不要啦 还是哥哥你来吧</p>
<p begin="7138300000t" end="7156300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle138">我只负责抓啦</p>
<p begin="7156300000t" end="7179300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle139">每次碰到麻烦你都丢给我</p>
<p begin="7227300000t" end="7256300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle140">啊 站住</p>
<p begin="7342300000t" end="7352300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle141">小狐狸</p>
<p begin="7394300000t" end="7419300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle142">我们还是别吃肉改吃鱼吧</p>
<p begin="7459300000t" end="7481300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle143">可怎么才能抓到鱼呀</p>
<p begin="7483300000t" end="7507300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle144">没竿没线也没钩啊</p>
<p begin="7597300000t" end="7623300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle145">没有食物 也没有火</p>
<p begin="7628300000t" end="7638300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle146">什么都没有</p>
<p begin="7640300000t" end="7651300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle147">别说啦</p>
<p begin="8012300000t" end="8027300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle148">讨厌</p>
<p begin="8032300000t" end="8051300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle149">你干嘛呀 哥哥</p>
<p begin="8150300000t" end="8160300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle150">哥哥</p>
<p begin="8215300000t" end="8242300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle151">呜哇 好酸</p>
<p begin="8304300000t" end="8325300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle152">我…还活着</p>
<p begin="8342300000t" end="8359300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle153">吃着蚂蚁而活着</p>
<p begin="8427300000t" end="8447300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle154">吃掉生命而活着</p>
