<p begin="9577300000t" end="9619300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle179">一切都处于看不见的洪流之中</p>
<p begin="9627300000t" end="9667300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle180">不知道这是不是就是宇宙或者世界</p>
